#This contains the easy task for spider
In the file that consists of the server files, we create a directory called pics. 
Where we will be storing and retriving our subsequent files
The database has a table called slideshow in the databased called hack.
It has 2 columns the id and the image column that has the filename of the image. 
CREATE TABLE 
slideshow
(id INT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT ,
image TEXT NOT NULL , 
PRIMARY KEY (id`));
